org.intermine.bio.io.gff3

Class GFF3Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.bio.io.gff3.GFF3Record

  • public class GFF3Record
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents one line of a GFF3 file. Some of this code is derived from BioJava.

        sequenceID - the sequence name
        source - the source
        type - the feature type
        start - the start coordinate on the sequence given by sequenceID
        end - the end coordinate on the sequence
        score - the feature score or null if there is no score
        strand - the feature strand or null
        phase - the phase or null
        attributes - a Map from attribute name to a List of attribute values
